title: Dishwasher Heating Element
description: Dishwasher Heating Element ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 8 Reviews PartSelect Number PS3653449 Manufacturer Part Number 154825001 This dishwasher heating element is not designed to heat the water that enters it, but is designed to maintain the heat of the water that enters the dishwasher. It is located on the bottom of the dishwasher. NOTE: Brass nuts are NOT included. Must be ordered separately.

installationInstructions.author: Denise from Burnt Hills, NY
installationInstructions.title: Heating element corroded, not heating
installationInstructions.content: Removed bottom plate and heating element brass nuts.  Disconnected heating element.  Connected new one then replaced brass nuts.  Put bottom plate back on.  Very easy.
